extraDescription: Services of a third party to perform the following activities: a?c Conduct a high-level, current state assessment of the roles and responsibilities of the various boards and committees and key stakeholders with decision-making authority vs. advisory roles related to Managed Web Services Governance (incl. planning, prioritization and oversight). a?c Identify gaps and risks of the current state, relative to Gartner research and established good practice.a?c Develop recommendations and provide TBS with the relevant tools and templates.
comments: This contract is a call-up against a Public Services and Procurement Canada procurement tool.
